  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Sirolimus in Kidney Transplant Recipients in India</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Post Marketing Surveillance Looking at Safety of Rapamune (Sirolimus) in Indian Population Undergoing de Novo Renal Transplantation.</official_title>
